\t</div>\n\t\t\n\t\t<a href=\"/wp-json/wp/v2/posts?per_page=100&#038;page=1&#038;status=publish%2Cdraft%2Cfuture%2Cpending%2Cprivate&#038;_fields=id%2Cslug%2Ctitle%2Cstatus%2Ccontent%2Cexcerpt%2Cfeatured_media%2Cdate%2Clink&#038;add-to-cart=23231\" aria-describedby=\"woocommerce_loop_add_to_cart_link_describedby_23231\" data-quantity=\"1\" class=\"button product_type_simple add_to_cart_button ajax_add_to_cart add-to-cart-loop\" data-product_id=\"23231\" data-product_sku=\"\" aria-label=\"Add to cart: &ldquo;Amethyst and Iolite Necklace&rdquo;\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-success_message=\"&ldquo;Amethyst and Iolite Necklace&rdquo; has been added to your cart\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"wd-action-icon\"><span class=\"wd-check-icon\"></span></span><span class=\"wd-action-text\">Add to cart</span></a>\t<span id=\"woocommerce_loop_add_to_cart_link_describedby_23231\" class=\"screen-reader-text\">\n\t\t\t</span>\n\t</div>\n\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQ About Crystals for Self-Love</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Can crystals help me love myself?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Not on their own. Crystals can&#8217;t grant self-love. Many people use them as tangible cues to be kinder to themselves; the practice of self-love is built through habits and, when needed, support like therapy.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Are crystals scientifically proven to boost self-love?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">No. There is no clinical evidence that crystals increase self-love or self-worth. Any felt benefit usually comes from the ritual of pausing and choosing a kinder thought, not a proven effect of the stone.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which crystal is best for self-love and self-compassion?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Rose quartz is the most commonly chosen — long tied to unconditional love and a gentle stance toward the self.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is the best crystal for self-worth and confidence?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Rhodonite and jade — rhodonite for compassion and forgiving yourself, jade for a steadier sense of worth.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which crystal helps when my inner critic is loud?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Amethyst and citrine — amethyst to quiet the mind, citrine for a warmer, sunnier self-regard.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How should I cleanse self-love crystals?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Smoke (sage, palo santo), sound (singing bowl), or moonlight work for most stones. Handle soft pieces gently and keep them dry.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is the best crystal bracelet for self-love?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">A rose quartz bracelet is the most common first choice — soft, widely available, and easy to wear daily as a reminder to be kind to yourself.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Explore More Crystal Guides</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-love/\">Crystals for Love</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-emotional-healing/\">Crystals for Emotional-healing</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-confidence/\">Crystals for Confidence</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-peace/\">Crystals for Peace</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-grief/\">Crystals for Grief</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Self-love is a practice, not a destination — and a real stone can be a steady cue to be on your own side. Start with one and let small kindness add up. For more, explore <a href=\"/love-relationships/\">Love &amp; Relationships</a>.</p>\n",
